      <Comment><![CDATA[Finds if a part is in a tray and what is the lowest index available]]></Comment>
      <Text><![CDATA[SBR(Scratch_Array,Temp_TrayPresent,Temp_DrawerClosed,Temp_DrawerLocked,Temp_string)NOP();]]></Text>
